      </processinfo>
      <arrangement id="aspace_479ddedb23248c66167d33c8d6b9d318">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Organized into three series: I. Correspondence, 1829-1867. II. Writings, 1809-18[64?]. III. Other Papers, 1809-1810.</p>
